news.title: No relief for Dehradun builder from Uttarakhand HC in land fraud case
news.para: Windlass's counsel said the 72-year-old was undergoing treatment for health complications at Himalayan Hospital in Dehradun, as per court directions.

news.title: Goa: ODPs case another indictment of TCP’s urban planning flaws
news.para: From putting on hold a circular on ODPs for the five villages to virtually striking down the TCP department’s power to unilaterally alter the zoning of private plots through Section 17(2) of the TCP Act, 1974, the courts have emerged as the battleground for Goa’s land politics.

news.title: Brookfield India REIT appoints Keki Mistry as independent director
news.para: The Board of Directors of Brookprop Management Services Pvt Ltd, the manager of Brookfield India Real Estate Trust, has approved the appointment of Keki Minoo Mistry as an additional director under the category of independent director.
